Hi <%= @order.customer_name %>,

Thank you for your order! We've received it and it's confirmed.

ORDER: <%= @order.order_number %>
Date: <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>

ITEMS
<% @order_items.each do |item| %>
  - <%= item.product_name %> (SKU: <%= item.product_sku %>) × <%= item.quantity %> — <%= number_to_currency(item.line_total) %><% if item.product %>
    <%= product_url(item.product) %><% end %>
<% end %>

Subtotal: <%= number_to_currency(@order.subtotal) %>
Shipping: <%= number_to_currency(@order.shipping_amount) %>
<% if @order.tax_amount > 0 %>
Tax:      <%= number_to_currency(@order.tax_amount) %>
<% end %>
Total:    <%= number_to_currency(@order.grand_total) %>

DELIVERY ADDRESS
<%= @order.shipping_address["full_name"] %>
<%= @order.shipping_address["street_address"] %>
<%= @order.shipping_address["city"] %>, <%= @order.shipping_address["state"] %> <%= @order.shipping_address["zip_code"] %>

We'll be in touch with delivery updates. If you have questions, reply to this email.

— Warehouse Furniture
